1
00:00:04,220 --> 00:00:07,730
<i> Where is it? I'm sure that I brought it.</i>

2
00:00:15,400 --> 00:00:18,720
Let's start class. What page are we on?

3
00:00:21,480 --> 00:00:23,780
Everyone who didn't bring your book to class stand up.

4
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:30,140
Han Yuho.

5
00:00:30,140 --> 00:00:32,460
You have English class every day, and you still forget to bring your English book?

6
00:00:32,460 --> 00:00:34,260
Stand there while lifting your chair up.

7
00:00:38,720 --> 00:00:40,780
<i> Yuho...</i>

8
00:00:40,780 --> 00:00:42,880
<i> You did that for me?</i>

9
00:00:45,210 --> 00:00:48,670
<i>[Ethics and Ideology] </i>

10
00:00:49,860 --> 00:00:52,900
<i> You gave me an Ethics textbook? </i>

11
00:00:55,620 --> 00:00:57,960
<i> [The Witch Store]</i>

12
00:01:00,100 --> 00:01:04,420
<i> [Episode 1] 
 [A Strange New Student]</i>

13
00:01:04,420 --> 00:01:07,260
♫ <i> Time out! You're cheating </i> ♫

14
00:01:07,900 --> 00:01:11,680
Teacher! I'm sorry.

15
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:14,520
I thought this was... Ethics class.

16
00:01:21,180 --> 00:01:23,700
<i> Don't be late for your part-time job today.</i>

17
00:01:23,700 --> 00:01:27,020
<i>She's so annoying first thing in the morning.</i>

18
00:01:32,240 --> 00:01:36,720
<i> Come as soon as school ends. If you're late, I will extend your job for one more day.</i>

19
00:01:36,720 --> 00:01:40,120
<i>There are exactly 9 hours and 33 minutes left. </i>

20
00:01:42,180 --> 00:01:45,020
<i> I've been working in the Witch Shop for five months.</i>

21
00:01:45,020 --> 00:01:48,420
<i> As you can see, this is my life now.</i>

22
00:01:52,240 --> 00:01:54,320
<i> 32 minutes.</i>

23
00:01:54,320 --> 00:01:56,360
My God!

24
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:59,960
<i> Let's be patient for two more months.</i>

25
00:02:06,800 --> 00:02:09,160
What's up with the mood?

26
00:02:09,160 --> 00:02:11,740
Oh... it's your work day today.

27
00:02:11,740 --> 00:02:15,120
There were no customers for the last five months. Should I even call it a part-time job?

28
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:17,760
She's obviously bored with her own life.

29
00:02:17,760 --> 00:02:21,560
She has no friends. She sent me 200 messages this morning alone.

30
00:02:22,920 --> 00:02:25,540
See? Another message from her.

31
00:02:25,540 --> 00:02:27,900
Be patient. Only two months to go.

32
00:02:27,900 --> 00:02:30,400
Also, it's good for you if there are no customers.

33
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:34,420
Then, you can go to work instead of me.

34
00:02:34,420 --> 00:02:36,760
Of course not. Good luck!

35
00:02:36,760 --> 00:02:38,620
Hi.

36
00:02:38,620 --> 00:02:42,560
- Eunah. 
 - Taeil.

37
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:44,256
I really hate that.

38
00:02:44,256 --> 00:02:46,020
You should date someone too.

39
00:02:46,020 --> 00:02:48,040
No, thanks. You go ahead and date as much as you like.

40
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:49,800
What about Yuho?

41
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:52,040
There must be other things better than the candy at that store.

42
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:54,940
Hey, I won't use anything from that shop.

43
00:02:54,940 --> 00:02:57,780
You said the same thing last time before using something.

44
00:02:57,780 --> 00:03:00,420
Get something using the employee discount.

45
00:03:00,420 --> 00:03:03,380
This is the time for you and Yuho...

46
00:03:03,380 --> 00:03:05,400
- What about me? 
 - What?

47
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:07,340
What? Actually...

48
00:03:07,340 --> 00:03:09,220
Hyeji said you have a cool phone case.

49
00:03:09,220 --> 00:03:11,580
Me? I don't have a phone case.

50
00:03:11,580 --> 00:03:14,660
Or was it Hyungseok's?

51
00:03:14,660 --> 00:03:17,680
- Hyeji, it was Hyungseok's phone case, not Yuho's.
 - Really?

52
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:19,520
I must have been confused.

53
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:22,060
- Yuho. 
 - What?

54
00:03:29,320 --> 00:03:31,419
Do you want to go to coin karaoke after school?

55
00:03:31,420 --> 00:03:33,060
School hasn't started yet and you are thinking about what to do after school?

56
00:03:33,060 --> 00:03:35,280
I'm planning in advance.

57
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:36,580
Eunah will definitely join us.

58
00:03:36,580 --> 00:03:39,580
If Eunah joins, Hyeji whom you all love will come too.

59
00:03:39,580 --> 00:03:41,880
- What? 
 - He's saying nonsense again.

60
00:03:41,880 --> 00:03:42,800
Hey!

61
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:46,840
Are you two really going to be like this? You said you like Hyeji.

62
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:50,120
True. Why did I do that?

63
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:52,400
What do you mean why? It's because you fall in love easily.

64
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:54,140
No, I'm not that kind of person.

65
00:03:54,140 --> 00:03:57,760
Hyeji is just a friend, right?

66
00:03:57,760 --> 00:04:02,380
What? Yes... She is just a friend.

67
00:04:06,820 --> 00:04:08,800
<i> [Ethics]</i>

68
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:10,380
The first period is English.

69
00:04:10,380 --> 00:04:13,800
Oh... I know. I'm just revising what I've learned.

70
00:04:18,660 --> 00:04:20,680
Hyeji, where are you going?

71
00:04:23,080 --> 00:04:24,840
Hyeji.

72
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:27,420
Where are you going? Don't you want to go to coin karaoke with the other kids?

73
00:04:27,420 --> 00:04:30,140
Oh... I heard it from Eunah.

74
00:04:30,140 --> 00:04:31,700
Are you going?

75
00:04:31,700 --> 00:04:34,160
I don't know. I thought about going if you are going.

76
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:35,720
Are you going somewhere after school?

77
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:37,879
No... Not exactly...

78
00:04:37,879 --> 00:04:41,970
- Then, let's go together. 
 - Oh... okay.

79
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:44,880
Wait.

80
00:04:44,880 --> 00:04:47,340
<i> Coin karaoke? You have a job to do.</i>

81
00:04:47,340 --> 00:04:49,980
<i> Please... Can I go just this once?</i>

82
00:04:49,980 --> 00:04:51,900
<i>Come here quickly. </i>

83
00:04:51,900 --> 00:04:53,820
<i> Can I go just for 30 minutes?</i>

84
00:04:53,820 --> 00:04:55,800
<i>Come quickly.</i>

85
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:57,600
<i> Ten minutes... or just five minutes?</i>

86
00:04:57,600 --> 00:05:02,100
<i> Hyeji, do you want to extend this job for another month?</i>

87
00:05:02,100 --> 00:05:05,300
Sorry. I can't go today.

88
00:05:05,300 --> 00:05:06,720
See you tomorrow.

89
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:09,610
Okay. Bye.

90
00:05:09,610 --> 00:05:13,530
♫ <i> Why are you turning a blind eye and ignoring it? </i> ♫

91
00:05:13,530 --> 00:05:17,880
♫ <i> I'll let you off easy today. It was so hard to get to this point</i> ♫

92
00:05:17,880 --> 00:05:20,000
<i> [The Witch Store] </i>

93
00:05:24,440 --> 00:05:26,060
<i> What?</i>

94
00:05:26,060 --> 00:05:28,880
<i> Am I in the wrong place? 
 [Witch Shop]</i>

95
00:05:36,900 --> 00:05:39,000
Hey, you are on time.

96
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,940
You should have had some fun with your friends first and taken your time coming here.

97
00:05:40,940 --> 00:05:42,760
Okay. Bye.

98
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:45,680
Where do you think you are going? What do you think about the new interior design?

99
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:47,560
Isn't it perfect?

100
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:49,500
Why did you change it all of a sudden?

101
00:05:49,500 --> 00:05:53,320
You said that the shop is too old-fashioned.

102
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:55,000
So, I changed it a little bit.

103
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:56,980
No. I said it looked awful.

104
00:05:56,980 --> 00:06:02,300
Anyway, reflecting on the opinion of my employee, I remodeled the shop in a trendy design.

105
00:06:02,300 --> 00:06:06,820
It's pretty but no one visits anyway.

106
00:06:06,820 --> 00:06:10,900
I told you. Only those with desperate wishes can come to this shop.

107
00:06:10,900 --> 00:06:13,400
Exactly like you.

108
00:06:13,400 --> 00:06:15,500
I shouldn't have entered the shop.

109
00:06:15,500 --> 00:06:20,339
Anyway, since only a few can come to this shop, you know what we need to do, right?

110
00:06:20,339 --> 00:06:23,380
Let's make a big fortune out of them.

111
00:06:25,500 --> 00:06:28,600
By the way, how do you know what I'm doing in class?

112
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:32,400
Do you spy on me through a magic crystal ball?

113
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:36,260
What? Who uses crystal ball these days?

114
00:06:41,900 --> 00:06:45,380
What are you doing? Go do some work.

115
00:06:46,620 --> 00:06:48,180
Okay...

116
00:06:58,480 --> 00:07:01,760
By the way, school looks fun.

117
00:07:01,760 --> 00:07:04,520
What? School is never fun.

118
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:07,980
I'll visit your school someday.

119
00:07:07,980 --> 00:07:10,800
Okay. Whatever. Come if you can.

120
00:07:11,980 --> 00:07:17,240
Hey, I'm young and beautiful compared to other witches.

121
00:07:19,880 --> 00:07:21,780
You don't believe it?

122
00:07:21,780 --> 00:07:25,200
Clean the corners too. I'm watching you.

123
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:27,620
I am cleaning.

124
00:07:29,380 --> 00:07:30,536
Did you have fun yesterday?

125
00:07:30,536 --> 00:07:33,940
No. We didn't have fun since you were not there.

126
00:07:33,940 --> 00:07:35,000
- Eunah. 
 - What?

127
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:38,820
Don't forget to pay me back for the tteokbokki, and the coin karaoke. Oh, and the carp bread too.

128
00:07:38,820 --> 00:07:42,620
Tteokbokki, coin karaoke and carp bread?

129
00:07:42,620 --> 00:07:44,340
So how was work yesterday?

130
00:07:44,340 --> 00:07:48,160
I don't know. She spies on me using drones.

131
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:49,820
I don't know where it is now.

132
00:07:49,820 --> 00:07:52,920
Drone? Where?

133
00:07:53,380 --> 00:07:56,140
- Hey! Isn't it that drone? 
 - Where?

134
00:07:57,100 --> 00:07:59,240
No, that's a bird.

135
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:00,820
Right... 
 <i>[2 - 1]</i>

136
00:08:07,860 --> 00:08:11,180
What? Who is that?

137
00:08:13,640 --> 00:08:16,720
Excuse me. Who are you?

138
00:08:18,220 --> 00:08:22,780
Hi, I'm a new student in class 1.

139
00:08:22,780 --> 00:08:25,680
Class 1? That's my class.

140
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:27,560
This is the first I'm hearing about that.

141
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:32,920
♫ <i> When I close my eyes, the magic starts</i> ♫

142
00:08:32,920 --> 00:08:35,559
Oh... I remember now.

143
00:08:35,560 --> 00:08:37,580
We have a new student joining today.

144
00:08:37,580 --> 00:08:40,400
Okay. Come in.

145
00:08:46,940 --> 00:08:49,340
Everyone.

146
00:08:49,340 --> 00:08:52,620
We have a new student today.

147
00:09:07,980 --> 00:09:10,540
Hi, my name is Yu Youngji.

148
00:09:10,540 --> 00:09:12,440
Nice to meet you.

149
00:09:13,100 --> 00:09:18,720
<i> Unexpected variables always bring unexpected results.</i>

150
00:09:18,720 --> 00:09:22,200
<i> Whether the results are good or bad.</i>

151
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:26,400
♫ <i> I didn't know what you would look like</i> ♫

152
00:09:26,400 --> 00:09:29,680
♫ <i> Like the sound of a gunshot in my mind</i> ♫

153
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:34,130
♫ <i> I understood what you were</i> ♫

154
00:09:34,130 --> 00:09:37,610
♫ <i> Can you feel it coming tonight?</i> ♫

155
00:09:37,610 --> 00:09:41,940
♫ <i> If you hold me in your arms</i> ♫

156
00:09:41,940 --> 00:09:45,920
♫ <i> 'Cause with you this lonely life </i> ♫
